item.title: Helllp, java is being gay
item.dc:creator: @dakota72421 dakota72421
item.description:
@dakota72421 wrote:

it did that to me too here is the solution, re-download the source (example: pimpscape) but dont click open click save then let it download then click open then go to your desktop and right click on your source (desktop is where the icons are like internet) then click “Extract here” then wait for it to do the load thingy then it will download a little folder it will say the name of your source and double click it then open up moparscape and leave the ip “127.0.0.1” and leave the port then go to the folder it download and look for “Runserver” then double click it then go to moparscape webclient and log in with a username and pass and if it dont work change the port to 5555!

p.s tell me if it worked! =)
